# Contact form → Gmail SMTP (App Password)
# The contact form posts to /api/contact, which emails the enquiry via Gmail.
#
# 1. Use a Google account with 2-Step Verification enabled.
# 2. Create an App Password: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
#    (choose "Mail" / "Other"), copy the 16-character password.
# 3. Copy this file to .env.local and fill in the values below.
#    On the host (Vercel/Netlify/etc.) set the same variables in the dashboard.

# The Gmail address that sends the enquiry emails
GMAIL_USER=bestandlessblinds@gmail.com

# The 16-character App Password (NOT your normal Gmail password)
GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD=

# Where enquiries are delivered (optional — defaults to GMAIL_USER)
CONTACT_TO=bestandlessblinds@gmail.com
